      <title>日本对日元过度波动发出新警告</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/japans-top-fx-diplomat-ready-respond-vs-excess-currency-volatility-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日元跌至交易员认为增加了货币干预可能性的水平后，日本最高货币外交官表示，日本随时准备采取适当行动来应对汇率过度波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/japans-top-fx-diplomat-ready-respond-vs-excess-currency-volatility-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 23:03:51 GMT</pubDate>
