    <item>
      <title>美国经济进入第一季度基础更加稳固</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-fourth-quarter-economic-growth-revised-slightly-lower-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国第四季度经济增长略有下降，但其构成比最初预期的要强得多，这对近期前景来说是个好兆头，尽管经济活动因低温而开局疲弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-fourth-quarter-economic-growth-revised-slightly-lower-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 13:47:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通胀数据公布，华尔街股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/futures-edge-lower-us-inflation-data-looms-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股市周三收盘小幅走低，一天前将公布关键通胀数据，该数据可能会严重影响人们对美联储降息时间的预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/futures-edge-lower-us-inflation-data-looms-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 10:56:27 GMT</pubDate>
